text: The number 172 is a natural number. It comes after 171 and before 173. == Mathematics == *172 is an even number because it can be divided by 2. *It is a composite number, which means it can be divided by numbers other than 1 and itself. The factors of 172 are 1, 2, 4, 43, 86, and 172. *The prime factorization of 172 is 2 × 2 × 43, or 2² × 43. Category:Integers
title: 172 (number)
